SD Card Reader Wiring Guide

Sensor -> Board

Arduino Uno
CS -> 10 (or any number, you just have to change the number in the code)
D1 -> 11
D0 -> 12
CLK -> 13
GND -> GND
5V -> 5V (or 3V -> 3.3V)

Arduino Mega
CS -> 10 (or any number, you just have to change the number in the code)
D1 -> 51
D0 -> 50
CLK -> 52
GND -> GND
5V -> 5V (or 3V -> 3.3V)
